translations.source: Duik needs to be allowed to write files to display its buttons, and to access the network to check for updates.
translations.translation: Duik需要文件写入权限以显示按钮，并需要连接网络来检查更新。

translations.source: Please, check the box called 'Allow Scripts to write files...' in the general preferences of After Effects.
translations.translation: 请在After Effects中的通用设置里勾选“允许脚本写入文件…”

translations.source:
A new version of Duik is available,
go to http://rainboxprod.coop to download it
translations.translation:
已发现新版的Duik，
前往 http://rainboxprod.coop 下载

translations.source:
UPDATE AVAILABLE -

A new version of Duik is available!
Version:
translations.translation:
已有升级可用 - 

新版Duik已可用！
版本号：

translations.source: Go to http://rainboxprod.coop to download it.

After Effects must be restarted

to complete the installation of Duik

May the god(s?) of animation be with you!
translations.translation:
After Effects需要重启

来完成Duik的安装

愿动画之神与你同在！

translations.source:
It seems Duik can not automatically install the pseudo effects it needs.

The easiest way to fix this is by restarting After Effects with administrator privileges,

or you can manually install the pseudo effects needed by Duik: click on the 'Next' button below.
translations.translation: Duik似乎无法自动安装所需伪特效：单击下方的“下一步”按钮。

translations.source:
Open the file 'presetEffects.xml':
Right click on
Applications/Adobe After Effects/Adobe After Effects.app,
Select 'Show package contents', go to
Contents/Resources/PresetEffects.xml.
translations.translation:
打开“presetEffects.xml”文件：
右键单击
Applications/Adobe After Effects/Adobe After Effects.app，
选择“显示包内容”，进入
Contents/Resources/PresetEffects.xml。

translations.source:
Open the file 'presetEffects.xml' :
C:\Program Files\Adobe\Adobe After Effects\Support Files\PresetEffects.xml.
translations.translation:
打开“presetEffects.xml”文件：
C:\Program Files\Adobe\Adobe After Effects\Support Files\PresetEffects.xml。

translations.source:
Copy the content of the box below,
hit Cmd+A
to select all the text,
then Cmd+C to copy it.
translations.translation:
拷贝下面文本框内的内容，
按cmd+A
全选文本，
然后按cmd+C来拷贝它。

translations.source:
Copy the content of the box below,
hit Ctrl+A
to select all the text,
then Ctrl+C to copy it.
translations.translation:
拷贝下面文本框内的内容，
按ctrl+A
全选文本，
然后按ctrl+C来拷贝它。

translations.source:
Paste this text in the file 'presetEffects.xml'
just BEFORE the last line: '</effects>'.
translations.translation:
在文件“presetEffects.xml”的最后一个“</effects>”的*上一行*
粘贴拷贝的内容

translations.source:
Oops!
Something is wrong, Duik can not find pseudo effects.

Go to http://www.duduf.net to get help.
translations.translation:
Oops！出错啦，Duik无法找到伪特效。

前往 http://www.duduf.net 获得帮助。

Be careful not to assign twice the same layer

Layers assigned twice:

请不要将同一图层绑定两次

绑定两次的图层：

translations.translation: 自动绑定对3D图层不起效
脊柱 和/或 髋关节

translations.source: Select the bones and the controller before creating IK
translations.translation: 选择骨节和控制器来创建IK

translations.source: Select the layer before applying IK Goal
translations.translation: 选择图层来创建IK目标约束
Duik - 显示隐藏的控制器

translations.source: Select a pin to create a bone
The layers are at the same place.
Select a layer to apply Zero
translations.translation: 选择一个图层以运用归零
Duik - 替换表达式中的名字

translations.source: You must specify a (unique) name for this instance of the rig
translations.translation: 在这个绑定中，你必须为其赋予不重复的名字

translations.source: Select the property where to apply the "wiggle" function
translations.translation: 选择需要执行“抖动”的属性

translations.source: Select two layers to measure distance from one layer to another!
translations.translation: 选择两个图层来测量它们间距离！

translations.source: What is the radius of the wheel?
Select all the layers of the lens flare, beginning by the center
translations.translation: 从光晕的中心开始，选择组成光晕的所有图层

translations.source: Cannot create expression on this effect
translations.translation: 无法在此效果上创建表达式

translations.source: Select the effect where you want to create the spring
translations.translation: 选择一个效果以创建回弹

translations.source: Please select the layers from which you want to save animation
translations.translation: 请选择需要保存动画的图层

translations.source: Selected layer is not a camera

translations.translation: Duik - 缩放-纵深 链接
Duik - 导入 TVPaint 摄像机

translations.source: Choose the camera file you want to import
translations.translation: 选择所需导入的摄像机文件
带有自动保存的简单的记事本。

translations.source: Warning, this is a version for testing purposes only!
translations.translation: 警告，这个版本仅做测试用！

translations.source: It may or may not be shipped with a lot of bugs.
translations.translation: 其可能包含大量的错误。

translations.source: A form is available at http://duiktest.duduf.net
translations.translation: 在 https://duiktest.duduf.net 上有一个列表

translations.source: to report bugs or make suggestions!
translations.translation: 来反馈错误和提出建议！

translations.source: If you need help using Duik,
translations.translation: 如果你在使用Duik时需要帮助，
下面的资源将十分的有用：

translations.source: Rainbox Forum, where you can ask your questions:
translations.translation: 可以用以提问的Rainbox的论坛

translations.source: Kevin Schires - Including images in the script
translations.translation: Kevin Schires - 将UI图片转换为文本格式

translations.source: Warning, interactive update can create a LOT of history items (Undos) and could easily fill up your entire history.
translations.translation: 警告，交互式更新会产生大量的历史记录（Undos），这很容易填满你的整个返回操作列表

translations.source:
Are you sure you want to activate interactive update?

Interactive update can create a LOT of history items (Undos) and could easily fill up your entire history.
translations.translation:
你确定要使用交互式更新？

交互式更新会产生大量的历史记录（Undos），这很容易填满你的整个返回操作列表

translations.source: Selected layer will keep its orientation, despite the transformations of its parent
translations.translation: 所选图层的轴向将无视父级变换而保持方向

translations.source: Move layers as a Bezier curve
translations.translation: 以贝塞尔曲线的方式移动图层

translations.source: 'Morphs' the property based on a layer rotation
translations.translation: 用一个图层的旋转来控制某个属性

translations.source: Creates a bone on a point of an effect
translations.translation: 在一个效果的锚点上创建骨骼

translations.source: Creates a "Zero" object on a layer
translations.translation: 为一个图层创建“归零”物体

translations.source: Adds an animation list on the property
translations.translation: 为选定属性创建动画列表

translations.source: Search and replace text in expressions
translations.translation: 搜索与替换表达式中的文本

translations.source: Automatically paste animation in the comp (using layer names)
translations.translation: （以图层名称的方式）在合成中（以图层名称的方式），自动粘贴动画

translations.source: Automatically imports a rig in the active comp, transfering the controllers and taking care of duplicates.
translations.translation: 自动将一个绑定导入活动的合成中，并添加好控制器，处理好重复的部件

translations.source: Create a wiggle function in a property of the selected layer
translations.translation: 在选定图层的一个属性上加上抖动效果

translations.source: Create an oscillation on the selected property
translations.translation: 给选定属性加上往复变化

translations.source: The property will automatically bounce like a spring
translations.translation: 属性值会像弹簧一样回弹

translations.source: Auto orientation of the layer along its path
translations.translation: 图层的旋转将自动跟随路径

translations.source: Automates the rotation of a wheel while moving the layer
translations.translation: 自动旋转轮子来贴合图层的位移

translations.source: Creates a lens flare with selected layers
translations.translation: 用选定的多个图层创建镜头光晕

translations.source: A simple controller to move away a layer from its parent
translations.translation: 将子物体沿着与父级相同的方位移动

translations.source: Links an effect with the distance with another layer
translations.translation: 用另一个图层的位移来控制一个效果

translations.source: Changes the exposure of the animation on the selected property
translations.translation: 修改选定属性的动画曝光表

translations.source: Rig the paint effects to be able to animate all strokes as if there was only one.
translations.translation: 将所有的笔触效果绑定为同一个动画方便K动画。

translations.source: Rig the paint effects to be able to animate selected strokes as if there was only one.
translations.translation: 将选定的笔触效果绑定为同一个动画方便K动画。

translations.source: Creates animation controllers for a camera
translations.translation: 为摄像机创建动画控制器

translations.source: Links the distance of the layer from the camera to its scale, so its apparent size won't change.
translations.translation: 将图层到摄像机的距离与图层的缩放链接起来，以保证图层比例不会改变

translations.source: Creates multiplane controllers to use as a 2D camera
translations.translation: 创建多平面控制器以便用2D摄像机来模拟空间
从 TVPaint 中导入相机

translations.source:
Warning! When controllers are locked,
they should be unlocked before parenting.
translations.translation:
警告！当控制器被锁定时，
它们在创建父子关系时必须先解锁

translations.source:
Unlock selected controllers
(all controllers if none selected)
translations.translation:
解锁所选控制器
（若没有选择则解锁所有控制器）

translations.source:
Lock selected controllers
(all controllers if none selected)
translations.translation:
锁定所选控制器
（若没有选择则锁定所有控制器）

translations.source:
Unhide selected controllers
(all controllers if none selected)
translations.translation:
显示所选控制器
（若没有选择则显示所有控制器）

translations.source:
Hide selected controllers
(all controllers if none selected)
translations.translation:
隐藏所选控制器
（若没有选择则隐藏所有控制器）
重置所选控制器的变换信息

translations.source: Lower accuracy can speed up analysis
translations.translation: 更低的准确度将提升分析速度

translations.source: Higher tolerance will result in higher exposure
translations.translation: 更大的容差度将得到更长的曝光时间
分析图层以得到曝光时间

translations.source: If enabled, creates cels as new paint effects on a single layer
translations.translation: 如果使用，创建的赛璐珞将成为单一层的一个新的笔触效果
创建3D多平面摄像机绑定
测量到另一个物体间的距离

translations.source: When the Spring is used on the position property of a layer,
translations.translation: 当回弹用在一个图层的位移属性上时，

translations.source: there are two ways to compute it:

translations.translation: 不进行解算 - 计算量小

translations.source: Needs an animation on the layer itself to work.
translations.translation: 需要该图层本身有动画才能起效。
进行解算 - 大量计算

translations.source: Works even if there is no animation on the layer, using the movement of the parent layers.
translations.translation: 即便该图层没有动画也起效，将使用父级运动进行解算。

translations.source: Resulting animation may be smoother too.
Horses, cattles, girafes, pigs, deers, camels, hippopotamuses...
translations.translation: 马，牛，长颈鹿，猪，鹿，骆驼，河马…

translations.source: Duik must be restarted to apply changes.
translations.translation: 必须重启Duik以使更改起效

translations.source:
Active composition not found.
Please select a composition or activate the composition panel.
translations.translation:
未找到激活的合成。
请选择一个合成或激活合成面板。

translations.source: Please be patient while Duik is doing its magic.
translations.translation: 请耐心等待Duik完成它的魔法
